<plot>Slices of life. Martin sleeps alone. He wakes each day and contemplates "what if?" He keeps a pistol near at hand in case he wants to leave his life. Sometimes, he lives his life in reverse. He thinks about his lost love. He works. In spite of the pain, he chooses to live another day.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?505680</url></doc>
